channel.title: Error_game_js5connect
channel.description:
[center][size=15pt]Welcome[/size] [size=7pt][i]error_game_js5connect[/i][/size]
[i]I've been having a few problems with a client i've been using. When I load up the client and enter the internet protocol the client opens up, then the loading bar reads 'Connecting to update server'. The loading bar then stops loading and in the command prompt an error message reads 'error_game_js5connect'.[/i]
[img]http://i31.tinypic.com/2mzvzmb.jpg[/img][/center]
